select "AV".*, "budget"."icon" as "dim_icon", "budget"."description" as "dim_description", "budget"."label" as "dim_label" from (select *, (select "path" from "AnalyticsSeries_AnalyticsDimension" as "ASAD" left join "AnalyticsDimension" as "AD" on "AD"."id" = "ASAD"."dimensionId" where "ASAD"."seriesId" = "AS_inner"."id" and "AD"."dimension" = 'budget') as "dim_budget" from "AnalyticsSeries" as "AS_inner" where "metric" in ('Actuals', 'PaymentsOnChain', 'ProtocolNetOutflow', 'Forecast') and "unit" in ('DAI') and "start" < '2025-01-01 00:00:00.000') AS "AV" left join "AnalyticsDimension" as "budget" on "budget"."path" = "dim_budget" where "dim_budget" like 'atlas/%' order by "start" asc

select "AV".*, "budget"."icon" as "dim_icon", "budget"."description" as "dim_description", "budget"."label" as "dim_label" from (select *, (select "path" from "AnalyticsSeries_AnalyticsDimension" as "ASAD" left join "AnalyticsDimension" as "AD" on "AD"."id" = "ASAD"."dimensionId" where "ASAD"."seriesId" = "AS_inner"."id" and "AD"."dimension" = 'budget') as "dim_budget" from "AnalyticsSeries" as "AS_inner" where "metric" in ('PaymentsOffChainIncluded') and "unit" in ('DAI') and "start" < '2025-01-01 00:00:00.000') AS "AV" left join "AnalyticsDimension" as "budget" on "budget"."path" = "dim_budget" where "dim_budget" like 'atlas/%' order by "start" asc

select "AV".*, "budget"."icon" as "dim_icon", "budget"."description" as "dim_description", "budget"."label" as "dim_label" from (select *, (select "path" from "AnalyticsSeries_AnalyticsDimension" as "ASAD" left join "AnalyticsDimension" as "AD" on "AD"."id" = "ASAD"."dimensionId" where "ASAD"."seriesId" = "AS_inner"."id" and "AD"."dimension" = 'budget') as "dim_budget" from "AnalyticsSeries" as "AS_inner" where "metric" in ('PaymentsOffChainIncluded') and "unit" in ('MKR') and "start" < '2025-01-01 00:00:00.000') AS "AV" left join "AnalyticsDimension" as "budget" on "budget"."path" = "dim_budget" where "dim_budget" like 'atlas/%' order by "start" asc

select "AV".*, "priceData"."icon" as "dim_icon", "priceData"."description" as "dim_description", "priceData"."label" as "dim_label" from (select *, (select "path" from "AnalyticsSeries_AnalyticsDimension" as "ASAD" left join "AnalyticsDimension" as "AD" on "AD"."id" = "ASAD"."dimensionId" where "ASAD"."seriesId" = "AS_inner"."id" and "AD"."dimension" = 'priceData') as "dim_priceData" from "AnalyticsSeries" as "AS_inner" where "metric" in ('DailyMkrPriceChange') and "unit" in ('DAI') and "start" < '2025-01-01 00:00:00.000') AS "AV" left join "AnalyticsDimension" as "priceData" on "priceData"."path" = "dim_priceData" where "dim_priceData" like 'atlas/%' order by "start" asc
